{
  "stem": "5837.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He has-- he had only a small apartment of two rooms, and he gave us one room, and he lived in the other one.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we lived with him for a year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[HEBREW] Rabin.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And a year later, you know, we moved to our own place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so I started-- when I came in 1950, I started elementary school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I went into second grade.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was the oldest kid in that grade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was there for about two months, and then my mother took me-- got me a private tutor during the summer, and I learned Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father-- of course, he was with us, and he got a job.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we had some family that had a textile store, and he worked as a salesman there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother immediately got a job as a doctor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we started our new life, you know, in Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after that summer, I took a test, and I guess my Hebrew was good enough.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I skipped third grade, went straight into fourth, and I was-- at that-- at the time, I was, like, on the same level of all the kids the same age.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the minute that my feet stepped on the-- in Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no way that you could not know you're Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a tremendous era of patriotism, of putting the-- what's good for the community before your own, you know, considerations.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "100% Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because certainly, I was not the only newcomer immigrant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was-- everybody was from somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I was not unique, speaking Polish at home and speaking Hebrew at school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, I wanted to less and less of the Polish, and I started to talk more and more of the Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
